WEBVTT

00:00:58.490 --> 00:01:00.095
Bugun siz kimsiz? Yoki

00:01:00.095 --> 00:01:01.383
besh yil oldim kim edingiz?

00:01:01.383 --> 00:01:03.402
Yoki 50 yildan keyin kim bo'lasiz?

00:01:03.402 --> 00:01:05.382
Va qachon "siz" borsiz?

00:01:05.382 --> 00:01:06.875
Shu haftadami?

00:01:06.875 --> 00:01:08.005
Bugunmi?

00:01:08.005 --> 00:01:09.143
Shu soatda?

00:01:09.143 --> 00:01:10.531
Shu soniyada?

00:01:10.531 --> 00:01:13.390
Va tanangizni qaysi qismi bulan "Men"siz?

00:01:13.390 --> 00:01:15.094
"Siz" - bu tashqi qobig'ingizmi?

00:01:15.094 --> 00:01:16.695
Fikrlaringiz va hislaringizmi?

00:01:16.695 --> 00:01:18.368
Qilgan ishlaringizmi?

00:01:18.368 --> 00:01:22.153
Mavhum mantiqning loyqa 
suvlarida suzish juda qiyin,

00:01:22.153 --> 00:01:25.752
shu sababli, ehtimol, ushbu masalaning 
murakkabligini ko'rsatish uchun,

00:01:25.752 --> 00:01:31.373
qadimgi yunon tarixchisi Plutarx 
'kema afsonasi'ni aytib bergan.